{
  "texts": [
    "Specifically, for each part of the ablation, we remove one specific module while keeping everything else the same.",
    "We utilize the FormNexus-GPT-4 given its superior performance shown in the previous sections.",
    "The ablation study is conducted across all applications listed in our dataset, and the averages are presented in Table 4.Effectiveness of FERG in Test Generation.",
    "By excluding the local textual context and relevant input context from the constraint and value generation prompts, we can quantify the extent to which FERG's information enhances the test generation results.Table 4 indicates that employing FERG and appending pertinent information to the prompt can bolster the state coverage from 82% to 89%, equating to a 9% improvement.",
    "Furthermore, the passing rate of the method increased from 70% to 83% by adding the FERG to the prompt."
  ]
